snippet.title: TED Tumblewords | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Slide rows of scrambled letters to spell words in this thought-provoking puzzle game from TED. Play every day to level up and set new high scores.

Play TED Tumblewords on your mobile devices. Available exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81718282

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

TED Tumblewords | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix
